    "long_instructions": "### Lullaby Song\r\n\r\n**Define:** A client has asked you to make a baby lullaby using classical music that helps them go to sleep. The song should gradually lower in volume before \"fading out\" tracks one at a time.\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Pick the tracks and effects you want to use and imagine what you want the timeline to look like. Consider how you want to plan the \"fade out\" effect!\r\n\r\n**Try:** Create your lullaby!\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** In order to pass this level, make sure your code has:\r\n- At least 6 tracks\r\n- At least 3 effects\r\n- A \"lowering\" volume and a fade out effect",
